8:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both AI Writer and Article Forge share a solid foundation of core features including Long Form, Seo Tools, Api Access. On the other hand, Article Forge uniquely offers Multilingual, giving it an edge for users who prioritize this area. \n\nLooking at user ratings, AI Writer holds an overall score of 5/10 and an ease of use score of 5/10, while Article Forge scores 4/10 overall and 8/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
9:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, Article Forge comes in at a lower starting price of $27/mo, while AI Writer begins at $29/mo. Neither platform offers a free plan, so you will need to budget for at least the starting tier from the beginning. Be sure to take advantage of any trial periods they may offer."}]]}]
